#: ../../source/chain/pir.rst:6 065faa286a0b408cbebe27243b998693
msgid ""
"PIRChain is the helper class for PIR (Passive Infrared) sensor devices on"
" the Chain bus. It provides methods to read IR induction values, "
"configure trigger delay, and monitor PIR trigger events."
msgstr ""
"PIRChain 是链式总线上 PIR（被动红外）传感器设备的辅助类。它提供了读取红外感应值、配置触发延迟以及监控 PIR 触发事件的方法。"

