msgid ""
"This example demonstrates how to use trigger callbacks from the Chain PIR"
" sensor to update motion status on screen. It enables trigger auto-send, "
"configures trigger hold time, and counts the detected duration while "
"motion is active."
msgstr ""
"本示例演示如何使用 Chain PIR 传感器的触发回调来更新屏幕上的运动状态。它启用触发自动发送、配置触发保持时间，并在运动激活时统计检测持续时间。"

